    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "48005016",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>信徒如何克制肉體的情慾？</strong></p><p>信徒可以依靠聖靈而活，因此不放縱肉體的情慾。</p>",
