    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "48006014",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>保羅說他為何感到驕傲？</strong></p><p>保羅說他為我們主耶穌基督的十字架而感到驕傲。</p>",
